Method	                            Description

length()	                        Returns length of the String
charAt(index)	                    Gets character at the given index
substring(start, end)	            Extracts a substring
toUpperCase()	                    Converts to uppercase
toLowerCase()	                    Converts to lowercase
concat(str)	                        Concatenates two strings
equals(str)	                        Compares content of two strings
indexOf(ch)	                        Returns first occurrence index of ch
replace(old, new)	                Replaces part of a String
trim()	                            Removes leading/trailing spaces
split(delimiter)	                Splits String into an array
StringBuffer	                    Mutable String (Thread-Safe)
StringBuilder	                    Mutable String (Fast, Not Thread-Safe)